            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099099/Van Dale groot woordenboek (1994)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>一種投擲式武器，基本上包含皮革、織物或類似的彈性材料，在中央展成一個小袋，用以放置拋射體。使用時握住兩端，快速環繞擺動，然後放掉一端將拋射體猛擲出去。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000079740/AS-Academia Sinica data (2014-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Tlen ica tlatehuia, tlachihualli ica mecatl tlem cuetlaxtli, yoyomitl zo ceyoc tlamantli yoyomitl tlen yamanic zo motilana, tlen mopatlahua itlahtotiyan quence folza para motlaliz ce tlamantli tetl tlen momahcahuaz. Moitzquiyza nochi ome itenno huan teipan momalacachoa chicahuac.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Eastern Huasteca Nahuatl</Note_Language>
